msgid "5500:さっきのは……僕の妄想だったの？[linebreak]どこまでが妄想で、どこからが現実？[%p]"
msgstr "5500:Was what I just experienced a delusion? How much was a delusion and how much was reality?[%p]"

msgid "5600:将軍に狙われていることや、日本中の笑い物になっちゃったのは、現実？[%p]"
msgstr "5600:Was Shogun still trying to kill me? Was the entire country laughing at me?[%p]"

msgid "5700:僕の気分は一瞬にして鬱へと転落していった。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:Instantly, I started to feel miserable and depressed.[%p]"

