msgstr "6900:[name]葉月[line]I heard that's what you told the police. They said you weren't making any sense. They couldn't get anything out of you.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]葉月[line]「[color index="A0FF0000"]心神喪失[color index="800000"]で無罪……っていうのを狙ってるんですか？」[%p]"
