msgid "10100:それとももしかして、僕が倒れたのは精神的要因って判断されたのかな？[%p]"
msgstr "10100:Or maybe they thought I had collapsed because of some mental disorder?[%p]"

msgid "10200:まあ……あながち、間違ってないけどさ……。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Well... if they did, they weren't that far off.[%p]"

