msgid "11500:これから先、平穏に生きていけるのかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:I might not ever have a peaceful life again.[%p]"

msgid "11600:ふと、脳裏に七海の顔が浮かんで。[linebreak]僕は唇を噛み、自分の膝を握りしめた。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:Suddenly, an image of Nanami's face flashed in my mind. I bit my lip and squeezed my hands against my thighs.[%p]"

