msgstr "11700:If I'd managed to save Nanami... none of that would've mattered.[%p]"

msgid "11800:たとえ僕が一生、世界中の人から“情けないヤツ”って鼻で笑われることになろうと、構わなかっただろう。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:The whole world could've laughed at me for the rest of my life, and I wouldn't have cared.[%p]"

msgid "11900:でも、僕は……[%p]"
msgstr "11900:But I...[%p]"

msgid "12000:七海を救うことすらできなかったんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I hadn't even been able to save her.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]拓巳[line]「なな…………う……う……」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]拓巳[line]Nana... Waaah...[%p]"

msgid "12200:ボロボロと、涙がこぼれた。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:The tears came pouring down face.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]葉月[line]「ど、どうしました？　どこか痛みます？」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]葉月[line]W-What's wrong? Does it hurt somewhere?[%p]"

msgid "12400:僕は何度もかぶりを振りながら、泣き続けた。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:I shook my head again and again as I cried.[%p]"

msgid "12500:七海は、死んだ。[linebreak]七海は、もう戻ってこない。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:Nanami was dead. Nanami wasn't coming back.[%p]"

msgid "12600:僕のせいだ。僕のせいだ。僕のせいだ。僕のせいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:It was my fault. It was my fault. It was my fault. It was my fault...[%p]"

msgid "12700:僕がヘタレだったから。[linebreak]七海は死んでしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:because I was such a loser. That's why Nanami had died.[%p]"

msgid "12800:あのとき、星来たん――に見せかけた僕の弱い心――の言葉にそそのかされて、僕はあっさりと、ディソードを手に入れることをあきらめた。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Up on that roof, I'd listened to Seira-tan—or rather, my heart's weakness talking to me through her—and given up on the Di-Sword without even really trying.[%p]"

msgid "12900:自分を可哀想な被害者に見立てて。七海を犠牲にしてまで、自分だけが生き残る道を選んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I'd chosen to save myself and pretend to be a poor little victim instead of saving her.[%p]"

msgid "13000:そんなヘタレな自分を、心から恨んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:I hated myself from the bottom of my heart.[%p]"

msgid "13100:もし、あのとき――[linebreak]もうちょっと頑張っていれば。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:If... when I was up there... If I'd tried a little harder...[%p]"

msgid "13200:自分自身の決断であきらめたって言うのに、すべてが終わってから過去を振り返って自分の行動を後悔する。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:I was the one who'd made the decision to give up, and yet I regretted it now that everything was over.[%p]"

msgid "13300:それこそ最悪だ。なんの救いにもならない。[linebreak]それでも、こう思わずにはいられないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:That was the worst possible thing a person could do. Regret didn't help anybody, but still, I couldn't help but think…[%p]"

msgid "13400:あのときに戻れるなら、もうちょっと頑張るのに――[%p]"
msgstr "13400:If I could go back to that moment, I'd try a little harder.[%p]"

msgid "13500:もっとも、いざ実際にあの場に戻されたら、きっとまたあれこれと言い訳をして、あきらめるんだろうな。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:But of course, even if I did go back, I'd probably make a bunch of excuses and give up again, anyway.[%p]"

msgid "13600:僕はいつだって、そうなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:That was what I always did.[%p]"

msgid "13700:ホントに、どうしようもないヤツなんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:God, I was pathetic.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「七海、ごめん……」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]Nanami, I'm sorry.[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]拓巳[line]「七海……う、ううっ……ぐすっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]拓巳[line]Nanami... Waaah.... Sob...[%p]"

msgid "14000:葉月さんが、僕をあやすように背中をさすってくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:Hazuki rubbed my back to comfort me.[%p]"

msgid "14100:僕はとことんダメな男だ。[linebreak]無関係な看護師さんにまで迷惑をかけちゃってる……。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I was such a failure. I was even causing trouble for this nurse, and she had nothing to do with it.[%p]"

msgid "14200:でも涙は止まってくれなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:But the tears kept coming.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]葉月[line]「なにか、後悔していることがあるんですね」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]葉月[line]There's something you regret, isn't there?[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]葉月[line]「でもきっと、妹さんも許してくれますよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]葉月[line]But don't worry. I'm sure your sister will forgive you.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………？」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]拓巳[line]...?[%p]"

msgid "14600:この人、なんで七海が僕の妹だって知ってるんだろう？[%p]"
msgstr "14600:How did she know Nanami was my sister?[%p]"

msgid "14700:それに、そんなありきたりな慰めの言葉なんていらなかった。葉月さんには悪いけど、どうせ他人には僕の気持ちなんて分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:And... I didn't want to hear something so clichéd. I hated to say this about Hazuki when she was being so nice to me, but there was no way she could understand how I felt.[%p]"

msgid "14800:僕は、ホントに、こんな自分がいやで、情けなくて、他人に甘えてばっかりで、自分のことしか考えてなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:I hated myself so much. I was so pathetic. I kept looking for other people to comfort me... when I only cared about myself.[%p]"

msgid "14900:こんな自分は、死ねばいいんだ……。[linebreak]もう、本気で死のうかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:I'd be better off dead. Maybe I really should kill myself.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]葉月[line]「昨日も、しきりに西條さんのことを心配していましたよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]葉月[line]She was really worried about you yesterday.[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]葉月[line]「とてもかわいらしい妹さんですね」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]葉月[line]Your younger sister is very cute, isn't she?[%p]"

msgid "15200:なにを言ってるんだ……？[%p]"
msgstr "15200:What was she talking about?[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]拓巳[line]「七海は……妹は……し、死に、ました……」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]拓巳[line]Nanami... my sister... is d-dead.[%p]"

msgid "15400:『将軍』に拉致されて。[linebreak]腕を切断されて。[linebreak]どこかに監禁されて。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Shogun had kidnapped her. He'd chopped off her arm. He'd locked her up somewhere.[%p]"

msgid "15500:最後はたぶん、ひとり寂しく死んでいったんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:And she'd probably died there, all by herself and lonely.[%p]"

msgid "15600:それを想像すると、僕の心は張り裂けそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:The thought of it made me feel like my heart would burst.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]葉月[line]「……そうなんですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]葉月[line]Is that right?[%p]"

msgid "15800:[name]葉月[line]「ごめんなさい、勘違いしてしまって……」[%p]"
msgstr "15800:[name]葉月[line]I'm sorry. I must've been mistaken.[%p]"

msgid "15900:今までずっと、七海のことをウザいって思ってた。[linebreak]でもやっぱり、１６年もずっと一緒に育ってきた、兄妹なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I'd always thought that Nanami was obnoxious. But thinking back, we'd been siblings for 16 years.[%p]"

msgid "16000:あいつはいつも、口では僕のことバカバカ言いながらも、僕の心配をしてくれていた。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:She'd always called me a jerk, but she'd always been worried about me.[%p]"

msgid "16100:いつも口うるさかったのだって、僕を自堕落な生活から抜け出させようとしてのことだったし。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:She was always so annoying because she was trying to break me out of my miserable life.[%p]"

msgid "16200:実家から差し入れを持ってきたときは、ただ僕によこすだけじゃなくて、必ず一緒に食べようとしてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:When she brought something to eat from home, she didn't just give it to me. She always tried to make sure we ate together.[%p]"

msgid "16300:普通、あの年齢の女子なら、僕みたいなキモい兄貴は完全無視するのが普通なのに。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:Normally, a girl that age would be trying her best to ignore a creepy older brother like me.[%p]"

msgid "16400:七海は、口は悪かったけど、ちゃんと話をしてくれた。僕の話も、聞いてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:Nanami might've been mean, but she'd always talked to me. She always listened to what I had to say.[%p]"

msgid "16500:学校でも、僕のことを避けるどころか、むしろ向こうから声をかけてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:At school, even, instead of ignoring me, she'd actively try to talk to me.[%p]"

msgid "16600:七海はいつだって、[linebreak]僕みたいな童貞のキモオタを、[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I was a pathetic, virgin otaku, but Nanami had always treated me...[%p]"

msgid "16700:ひとりの兄として、[linebreak]ひとりの人間として、[%p]"
msgstr "16700:treated me like... Like I was her brother.[%p]"

msgid "16800:見ていてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:Like I was a person.[%p]"

msgid "16900:あいつの存在が、僕にとってはすごく救いになってたんだ。[linebreak]今さら気付いても、遅いけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:She was one of the few things that kept me going. Realizing that when it was too late didn't change anything, though.[%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]葉月[line]「でも、だとしたら“おにぃ”ってどういう意味なのかしら……？」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]葉月[line]But what did she mean by “brother,” then?[%p]"

msgid "17100:……………………え？[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Huh?[%p]"

msgid "17200:[name]拓巳[line]「……え？」[%p]"
msgstr "17200:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "17300:言葉の意味がよく理解できなくて、僕は顔を上げた。[linebreak]涙でにじんで、葉月さんの表情はよく見えない。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:I looked up, unsure of what she meant. My eyes were so teary, I couldn't see the look on her face.[%p]"

msgid "17400:今、この人は、なんて言った？[%p]"
msgstr "17400:What had she just said?[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]葉月[line]「眠っている西條さんを“おにぃ、おにぃ”と[linebreak]何度も呼んでいたから……その印象が強くて」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]葉月[line]She kept calling you “brother” while you were asleep. Over and over again. It really stuck with me.[%p]"

msgid "17600:僕をそんな風に呼ぶ人間は……[%p]"
msgstr "17600:There was only one person...[%p]"

msgid "17700:ひとりしかいない……！[%p]"
msgstr "17700:who called me that![%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そ、そ、それっ、ほ、ホント、ですか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]拓巳[line]I-Is t-that true?![%p]"

msgid "17900:思わずベッドから立ち上がり、葉月さんに詰め寄ってしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I was so excited that I got out of bed and went over to her.[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]葉月[line]「は、はい？　なにがです？」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]葉月[line]I-I'm sorry? Is what true?[%p]"

msgid "18100:[name]拓巳[line]「な、な、七海が！？　い、妹が、七海が、ここに、き、来てたんですか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]拓巳[line]N-Nanami? My little sister... c-came here?[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]葉月[line]「いえ、その……はっきりお名前を聞いたわけでは……」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]葉月[line]No, I didn't get her name.[%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕、僕のこと、おにぃって、よ、呼んでたんですね！？」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]拓巳[line]But she was calling me “brother,” right?[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]葉月[line]「え、ええ……」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]葉月[line]Y-Yes.[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なな、七海は、い、今どこに！？」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]拓巳[line]W-Where is Nanami now?[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]葉月[line]「で、ですから、昨日はお帰りになりましたけど……」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]葉月[line]I-I told you, she went home last night.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]葉月[line]「西條さんの、お母様と、一緒に……」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]葉月[line]Her and your mom.[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]拓巳[line]「ケガ！　ケガとか、し、してませんでしたか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]拓巳[line]Was she hurt? W-Was Nanami hurt?[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]葉月[line]「はい？　いえ、特には……」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]葉月[line]I'm sorry? No, not in any way that I could see.[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]拓巳[line]「元気だったん、で、ですね！？[linebreak]七海は、げ、元気だったんですね！？」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]拓巳[line]W-Was she doing okay? S-She was doing okay, right?![%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]葉月[line]「は、はい……あ、いえ、七海さんかどうかは分かりませんけど。昨日いらしていた女の子は、元気そうでしたよ」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]葉月[line]Y-Yes... Well, I don't know if the girl I saw yesterday was Nanami. But the one who was here seemed to be just fine.[%p]"

msgid "19200:……七海が、生きてる。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:Nanami was alive.[%p]"

msgid "19300:葉月さんの言葉を聞く限り、間違いなさそう。[linebreak]僕はほとんど放心状態になって、ベッドに腰を下ろした。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:From what Hazuki was saying, that much seemed clear. I sat back down on the bed. My brain was close to total shutdown.[%p]"

msgid "19400:いったい、どうして？[%p]"
msgstr "19400:What had happened?[%p]"

msgid "19500:『将軍』は、クエストをクリアしないと七海は返さないって言ってたのに。[linebreak]まさか同情して解放してくれたの？[%p]"
msgstr "19500:Shogun said he wouldn't give Nanami back unless I finished the quest. Had he released her out of pity? Was that even possible?[%p]"

msgid "19600:それとも七海が自力で逃げ出してきた？[%p]"
msgstr "19600:Or had she run away on her own?[%p]"

msgid "19700:でも、じゃあ僕のところに送られてきた、あの手首はどう説明する？[%p]"
msgstr "19700:But then what about the hand that had shown up in my room?[%p]"

msgid "19800:葉月さんの話じゃ、七海はケガさえしてないらしいじゃないか。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:Hazuki had even said she wasn't hurt.[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]将軍[line]「もしかしたら、キミの家に送ったあの手首は、別人のものかもしれないよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]将軍[line]That might've been somebody else's wrist, you know.[%p]"

msgid "20000:あの言葉は、ウソじゃなかったんだ……。[linebreak]僕は、『将軍』の手の平の上で踊らされてただけ。[%p]"
msgstr "20000:So he wasn't lying when he said that. Shogun had just been toying with me.[%p]"

msgid "20100:騙されていただけなんだ……。[linebreak]いや、騙されてたことは今はどうでもいい。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:He'd deceived me. No, the fact that he deceived me didn't even matter now.[%p]"

msgid "20200:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そっかぁ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20200:[name]拓巳[line]I-I see.[%p]"

msgid "20300:そうか、そうだったんだ……。[linebreak]そうだったんだよ。[%p]"
msgstr "20300:So, she was okay. She was okay... She was okay.[%p]"

msgid "20400:七海は、最初から拉致されてなんていなかったんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "20400:Nanami had never been kidnapped in the first place![%p]"

msgid "20500:Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴで僕が必死にディソードをつかもうとしてるとき、[linebreak]きっと七海は家でのんびりマンガでも読んでたか、友達とカラオケ[linebreak]にでも行ってヘタクソな歌声を披露してたに違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:While I was on top of O-FRONT trying to grab that Di-Sword, she was probably at home, reading manga in bed, or going to karaoke with her friends and singing off key.[%p]"

msgid "20600:[name]拓巳[line]「は、ははは……ぐすっ、はは……」[%p]"
msgstr "20600:[name]拓巳[line]Hah... Hahaha... Sob... Haha...[%p]"

msgid "20700:泣いていたのに、笑いがこみ上げてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:I was crying, but I couldn't stop laughing.[%p]"

msgid "20800:[name]葉月[line]「に、西條さん？」[%p]"
msgstr "20800:[name]葉月[line]N-Nishijo?[%p]"

msgid "20900:[name]拓巳[line]「はは、しょ、『将軍』に……ま、まんまと騙された……ぐすっ、ははは……」[%p]"
msgstr "20900:[name]拓巳[line]Hahah... S-Shogun really got me good... Sob... Hahaha...[%p]"

msgid "21000:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なんという、壮大な、釣りだよ、はは……」[%p]"
msgstr "21000:[name]拓巳[line]Man... talk about an epic troll.[%p]"

msgid "21100:七海は、生きてる。[linebreak]生きてるんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Nanami was alive. She was alive![%p]"

msgid "21200:またあのクソ生意気な顔を見られる。[%p]"
msgstr "21200:I'd get to see her bratty face again.[%p]"

msgid "21300:あのきゃんきゃんうるさい声を聞ける。[%p]"
msgstr "21300:Hear her obnoxious voice again...[%p]"

msgid "21400:そう思うと、心の底から安堵し、嬉しさがこみ上げてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "21400:I felt so relieved, and so happy.[%p]"

msgid "21500:[name]拓巳[line]「よかった……」[%p]"
msgstr "21500:[name]拓巳[line]I'm so glad.[%p]"

msgid "21600:涙が止まらない。[linebreak]でもこの涙は、さっきまでの悔し涙じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "21600:The tears wouldn't stop. But they weren't the tears of frustration I'd been weeping a moment ago.[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]拓巳[line]「よか、った……ううう……」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]拓巳[line]I'm so glad... Sob...[%p]"

msgid "21800:僕はどうしようもなくダメなヤツだけど。[linebreak]昨日も、結局自力でなんとかすることなくあきらめちゃったけど。[%p]"
msgstr "21800:Maybe I was total failure. Maybe I'd given up on trying to save Nanami on my own yesterday.[%p]"

msgid "21900:それでも、七海さえ生きてるなら、それ以上のことなんて求めない。[linebreak]世界中からあざ笑われたって、構うもんか。[%p]"
msgstr "21900:But as long as she was safe, that was all that mattered. The whole world could laugh at me, and I wouldn't care.[%p]"

msgid "22000:ホントに、よかった……。[%p]"
msgstr "22000:Really... I was just so happy.[%p]"

